{"tid":1630350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"運動點走落去呀？","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:05:47.000Z","uid":138050,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e17f1750d63e01438f394a16dc921c6dfcadff0a","tid":1630350,"uid":138050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j0EE5S6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj0EE5S6.png&h=f8c81f23&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2d37f58fb449f590acce10e857200dcd63d74f4f","tid":1630350,"uid":138050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:13:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十一 拆中資咁開心 玩埋今晚證明佢條緊急法蒙面法嚇唔到我地之係真係要好好諗下</span>"},{"pid":"3fee2289922239f07fee17421843af6666f66896","tid":1630350,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:13:28.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4c02cad29798dcc9b8eba896954c2bda9c3bd35","tid":1630350,"uid":138050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d37f58fb449f590acce10e857200dcd63d74f4f","tid":1630350,"uid":138050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:13:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十一 拆中資咁開心 玩埋今晚證明佢條緊急法蒙面法嚇唔到我地之係真係要好好諗下</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"*後"},{"pid":"7171486dfe734b3ade57d1c5547b91abe7cfa1d0","tid":1630350,"uid":138050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4abf7a6c0d2ef6177932d0b8916f7297ea96f545","tid":1630350,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:15:38.000Z","msg":"變返係商場唱歌算?"},{"pid":"d6139c0fd9fac00b38f909d6fde1d90563820740","tid":1630350,"uid":249794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:19.000Z","msg":"其實今日遊行冇狗就冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd122ae7973a8b5b01def2ef8c03c1494ef63f43","tid":1630350,"uid":246422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"！唔該小心你屋企樓下個看更！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630285</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6559c8dbbc4d4ddc55c07df3a522058c63f7326","tid":1630350,"uid":299523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e17f1750d63e01438f394a16dc921c6dfcadff0a","tid":1630350,"uid":138050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j0EE5S6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj0EE5S6.png&h=f8c81f23&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"我一定係路線3"},{"pid":"07bf7100cc0c54046ba46fbb9af05372fdd260eb","t